  "firstAcquaintance": "An elf who patrols the area around the elven forest. She is particularly enthusiastic about this duty, as if searching for something.",
  "personality": "A gentle older-sister type who will smile while drawing her bow to dispatch enemies. She has some rather unspeakable private interests.",
  "like": "Erotic books",
  "familiarData": "Avril is a nimble elven patrol soldier skilled at using the forest for concealment. She can quickly climb trees to reach vantage points and loose accurate arrows from various poses.\nBeyond driving off intruders, patrol soldiers also confiscate all of their belongings as a lesson. Anything from outside the village is classified as \"contraband.\" As a patrol soldier, Avril is one of the contraband managers, and it was through this role that she came across erotic books, opening up a whole new world for her.\n\nSince then, Avril has been enthusiastically driving back intruders and seizing more contraband. Sometimes she can't help but act out scenes from her books, creating openings in her defense. However, thanks to the elves' fearsome reputation, most enemies just assume it's a terrifying trap and flee as fast as they can.\n\nThe plants on her body exist in a symbiotic relationship with her, constantly maintaining their blooming state. She can conjure countless plant arrows and adjust the size of her bow for whatever the situation calls for.",
